Line5.BAE4.Rog: They’ve suffered hardship before, but they’ve always clung on. Endured. As long as even one remains, so will the order and its traditions.
Line7.6D03F: Heard some rumors that the years have not been kind to them.
Line1.6D03F: Not sure. As far as I knew, it was under the protection of the old rogue order—the Sisters of the Sightless Eye.
MenuLabel: “How did Elias get a hold of the Sightless Eye?”
